@50013 = ~We have found a room where yuan-ti make histachi brew. Now we need to replace the mandrake root they use in the process with the root modified by Niro.~
@50014 = ~The Mandala Soul took us to a room where he dropped Niro's modified mandrake root before he died and we found this root.~
@50015 = ~We have replaced the Mandrake Root used in the Yuan-ti Histachi Brew with Nero's Modified Root. Now we just have to wait until the weaker broth is made.~
