@50017 = ~A weaker histachi brew has just been created. Now we need to replace the modified root with a regular one to hide the deception.~
@50018 = ~You managed to escape the crumbling fortress.~
@50019 = ~As a shaman, I know that if Zeym kills himself, he will not be resurrected. However, we can invoke his spirit and talk to him.~
